## 🔵 LAYER 1 — Root / Orchestration

### `package.json` (root)
The **monorepo controller**. Delegates commands:
- `npm run dev` → starts the backend server
- `npm run mongo:local` → launches local MongoDB via PowerShell
- `npm start` → runs `start-shms.ps1` which boots everything together

### `start-shms.ps1` / `local-run.bat`
Launch scripts that start MongoDB and the Node server together in one click.

### `scripts/` (root-level)
- **`start-local-mongo.ps1`** — Downloads and boots a portable MongoDB binary in `backend/.mongodb-bin/`
- **`stop-local-mongo.ps1`** — Reads `backend/mongod.pid` and kills the process
- **`mongo-status.ps1`** — Checks if MongoDB is running

